  <p><b><span id="Facilities_Manager">Facilities Manager - Process Owner</span></b> </p>
  <ul>
    <li>The Facilities Manager is responsible for managing the physical environment where the IT infrastructure is located.</li>
    <li>This includes all aspects of managing the physical environment, for example power and cooling, building access management, and environmental monitoring.</li>
  </ul>
